PLACEHOLDER - Please replace this file with your actual Super Admin Dashboard screenshot image.

To add your dashboard image:
1. Save your dashboard screenshot as 'admin-dashboard.png'
2. Place it in the 'usama-portfolio/src/assets/' folder
3. Replace this placeholder file

The image should ideally be:
- Format: PNG or JPG
- Dimensions: Around 1200x900 pixels (4:3 aspect ratio works best)
- Shows the main dashboard interface clearly
